data.description:
New price following unofficial appraisal!!!
This home is absolutely perfect! Total remodeling is already completed for you! Check out the beautiful granite countertops, the newer appliances including refrigerator remains. Large living room with cathedral ceiling and ceiling fan. Laundry room with additional pantry space. 2 full bathrooms. 3 good sized bedrooms. Primary suite has a gorgeous barn door to the bathroom. Full attic with 2 access areas. New LVP flooring throughout for super easy care. This one owner home has been meticulously maintained. And just wait until you see that beautiful front porch. You will definitely want to grab some sweet tea and sit a spell. Also, could easily be made handicapped accessible if needed. Large yard space and garden space too! No HOA!! Come check it out now!
